The Sky at Night - A Journey through Space and Time (TVRip)

Science Documentary hosted by Patrick Moore, published by BBC broadcasted as part of BBC The Sky at Night series in 2005 - English narration 
http://docuwiki.net/images/6/66/The-Sky-at-Night-A-Journey-through-Space-and-Time-TVRip-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------

Sir Patrick Moore presents a retrospective of five decades of The Sky ay Night, recalling the history of space exploration from the first Russian Sputnik, the major astronomical discoveries over half a century, and the people he has met, from Orville Wright to Neil Armstrong.
